Author: ottopk
Title: [ANN][ICO] ğŸ›° Decibels ğŸ›° - Decentralized Digital Royalties System
Body: Decibels is a provider of multi-media encryption and delivery on the Blockchain.  The digital era has greatly reduced the income potential for creators of music, media, and digital files. Torrent technologies and pirating of information have rendered the storage of digital files on computers unsafe, and data leakage is resulting in lower values for both data and creative media, severely crippling the online entertainment industry.  Decibels is a leading innovator in the movement to reclaim ownership and control of music and media for their creators, by tapping into the security, scale, and speed of the Blockchain network to establish an entirely new digital era of music, media sales, and advertising. Backed by the speed and exponential growth of the Ethereum Blockchain, Decibels is developing an optimum ecosystem for growth in the media world, together with a secure personal experience tailored to the entrepreneurial and artistic mindset.  Decibels was founded by creators, for creators, and bridges the divide between digital content providers and their customers by introducing a market approach to the online media industry, allowing creators to establish and develop markets for their content, while providing their customers the opportunity to participate in the content's price determination, thus decentralizing the process of online media content valuation.  It is very interesting!

Title: [ANN][ICO] ğŸ›° Decibels ğŸ›° - Decentralized Digital Royalties System
Body: Good Morning/Evening Decibels Community,  Thank you for your patience with us while we handle everything needed to ensure a successful bounty program payout. To answer some questions for you guys, I know we have kept you a bit in the dark about prizes and we will update you all as often as we can.  1. Is the Bounty/Airdrop program still running? Currently the Vyper.IO URL you all have been using as the Bounty Round 1 is currently FINISHED. We have had over 30,000 submissions, and 11,000 winners who have completed necessary tasks to receive a prize. We are more than pleased with the results and can only hope that our community continues their support as often as possible.  2. What about Sylonâ€™s Bounty on BitcoinTalk?  Sylonâ€™s Bounty is ongoing and is Round 2 of the Bounty program. We offer all of you the chance to join in and continue sharing and promoting the growth of Decibels. We are hoping to reach over 100,000 members within our token holder count as we have the capacity and desire to be the most community driven token of 2018. We are currently at 23,000 token holders POST token distribution (meaning we havenâ€™t sent out tokens yet and they will be disbursed)  3. How do I get my tokens/prizes?  To receive your tokens please head on over to https://www.decibels.io/ico/ and register your account with your email you used on the vyper.io panel. It does not need to be this email as you can set your social links and we will find you and verity the wallet address to it.  4. When can I withdraw tokens from the ICO Panel? All members can begin withdrawing their bounty and purchased tokens from the system once token distribution date or hard cap value is met. We may extend the ICO Date to be prepared to wait a little bit longer. We have maintained ALL Records and will not miss a single payment. You can be sure of it and can ask us at ANY time in the chat to verify your amount of entries by your email, wallet address, or social media account!  5. How do I purchase Tokens?  Head on over to the ICO System and purchase your tokens with ETH, BTC, BCH, ETC, XRP, TRX, or 25+ other currencies! Our approach is highly different from our competitors though, where they seek to launch a platform that is utilized by consumers, we seek to use already established platforms such as youtube for our development. We are one of the only Media Developments that actually has real iconic record label backing, and real publicly followed artists with huge followings. Unlike most ICO's, we prefer NOT to display who we work with as this is just a tactic to build hype and show in this ICO World. Instead, we plan to offer our ICO to the people who understand how a development works and how profitable it is to enter at a phase like this. We will be the most community driven ICO as our supporters are large artists with large followings of 50k-500k+ including several artists with 1M+ member followings. This is just a start, and we have plenty more to come. We are supported by one of the best advisors there is and we are backed by several public youth organizations focused around art and creativity within kids and how art can effect their growth.

Author: coingrindr
Title: [ANN][ICO] ğŸ›° Decibels ğŸ›° - Decentralized Digital Royalties System
Body: What a great project and bounty program :  A Decentralized Media Revolution Based on Ethereum  Decibels is a blockchain solution to music and media encryptions and their delivery. This isnâ€™t another utility token of the future, it is a product for a community that will improve your life now. Decibels is leaving the blockchain development to Cardano and Ethereum while they are focusing on developing a media-based decentralized application to work with those developments.  How can Decibels improve your life?  Music and media files overwhelm virtual storage areas and the ability to torrent and pirate information has made keeping these files on devices unsafe. For the consumer, the issue is the security vulnerabilities consuming media brings to their technology. For creators, it is leaks and pirating that are detrimental to the value of the art and media they have produced. Leaks innately lower the worth of entertainment, harming creators. Decibels wants to lead a music/media revival by integrating security, scalability, and speed of the blockchain network to bring in a new digital era of music/media sales and advertising.  Based on the speed and continued growth of the Ethereum Network, Decibels seeks to secure a personal experience within a perfect ecosystem that allows for growth in the media world.  How will Decibels decentralize the value of media?  Decibels serves to bridge the gap between creator and audience by introducing a market-model to the media industry, meaning that creators can make their own content markets to give their fans, audiences, and communities a way to determine their own worth. Decentralizing the value of media content will be beneficial to creators and consumers.  Decibels is designed to mitigate, and eventually, remove the worry of piracy and media theft. Key developments for hardware, software, and a digital application will be implemented with the aid of the ICO. The end benefitâ€”creating a secure media exchange that will be transferable via a Wallet Address to all your associated devices.  Who is the target audience?  Decibels is designed by creators, for creators. It is made for musicians, artists, designers, directors, developers, producers, filmmakers, journalists, authors, doctors, architects, and media lovers, right on down to the average college student.  The Decibels Team  Decibels is a multicultural and international development team with a dedication to innovation and a new kind of customer service. Based in both Northern America and Asia, Decibels is constantly growing to reach every corner of the globe from Central and South America to Africa to the United Kingdom and more. The Founder and Developer has been interested in cryptocurrency and creating personal Dapp samples since 2015. They are ready to execute the development goals on their roadmap to start a decentralized media renaissance.  About Decibelâ€™s ICO Sale  Decibelsâ€™ ICO sale is from March 1 â€“ May 10 and will have three constantly progressing amounts and time frames within that period. The purpose of having stages is to introduce fair market rates once the coin enters the 13 different (already applied for) exchanges. This will prevent the market value from being diminished after any initial sell-offs.

Body: NEXT-GEN DECENTRALIZED DIGITAL ROYALTIES SYSTEM   ICO is on HOLD  WEBSITE / WHITE PAPER / TELEGRAM / TWITTER / INSTAGRAM  Official Decibels Bounty campaign: 1 000 000 DCBL Tokens are waiting for you! https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=3102284 ======================================== ICO CAP  Softcap: 4 000 ETH Hardcap: 20 000 ETH    TOKEN SALE: 01.03.2018 - 09.05.2018  ICO Phase 1: 08.03 - 20.03 | 1 DCBL = $0.05 USD ICO Phase 2: 21.03 - 09.04 | 1 DCBL = $0.10 USD ICO Phase 1: 10.04 - 09.05 | 1 DCBL = $0.15 USD ======================================== Other Languages (Links will be updated after the translation) ------------------ . â€¢ Korean : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Indonesian : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Dutch : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Thai : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Polish : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Filipino: (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Japanese : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Vietnamese : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Italian : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Danish : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Russian: (ANN,Whitepaper) â€¢ Arabic: (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Spanish : (ANN, Whitepaper ) â€¢ Romanian : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Bulgarian : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Greek : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Turkish: (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Croatian : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ German : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Portuguese : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Slovenian : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Hindi : (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ French: (ANN, Whitepaper) â€¢ Chinese Simplified : (ANN, Whitepaper)  PROBLEMS ______________   Current Digital Royalties platforms do not offer transparency, scalability, or security for their clients earnings due to old database style payment systems. This has caused artists value to demise over time due to no transparency within the music digital royalties market.  SOLUTIONS ______________   Decibels is a leading innovator in the movement to reclaim ownership and control of music and media for their creators, by tapping into the security, scale, and speed of the Blockchain network to establish an entirely new digital era of music, media sales, and advertising. Backed by the speed and exponential growth of the Ethereum Blockchain, Decibels is developing an optimum ecosystem for growth in the media world, together with a secure personal experience tailored to the entrepreneurial and artistic mindset.  HOW IT WORKS ______________   Decibels was founded by creators, for creators, and bridges the divide between digital content providers and their customers by introducing a market approach to the online media industry, allowing creators to establish and develop markets for their content, while providing their customers the opportunity to participate in the content's price determination, thus decentralizing the process of online media content valuation.    1 - Jet-Stream Sales Platform Decibels provides an easy to use Jet-Stream sales process that allows all creators to develop customized markets for their files. Sales can be generated easily with Decibels's mainstream platform that connects all files of creators to high-traffic media platforms, such as YouTube and Vimeo!    2 - Easy Conversion of Earnings Decibels integrates a simple atomic swap feature that allows users to receive payments in Decibels (DCBL tokens) and then exchange them for any tokens that support atomic swap exchanges. It has never been easier to secure, market, and earn money from digital files in a easy clean environment!    3 - Secure System for File Upload Through use of the secure ledger properties of the Blockchain, Decibels creates immutable DApp applications that support high-priority payment and withdrawal transactions that are irreversible. This technology ensures that customer sales conducted on the Decibels platform are secure, and that the value of customer files can not be changed by anyone other than the creator of the files!    4 - Online Wallet and Bank Decibels is partnering with top crypto wallet developers and debit card companies to offer Decibels creators direct access to their earnings through ATM and NFC Payment (touchless payment) applications! This means no more waiting for checks or bank deposits to arrive. Creators can use their earnings immediately, or invest them back into their customer markets for growth and expansion!   DECIBELS USE CASE ______________    1. Register with Decibels Media Creators get started by registering with Decibels Media via the Decibels PC or Mobile Application. Creators will then undergo KYC Verification (legal compliance requirements) to gather information necessary for copyright and ownership rights for their files.  2. Complete Verification Process Upon passing verification, members can develop their creator profile, and select which form of media they will be offering, or they may create a multi-media platform that can be distributed to all mainstream platforms that accept their file type.  3. Upload media files and secure them with Decibels Members will then upload their files directly, or through third-party plugins such as Pro Tools and Reason, allowing for an immediate import into the file vault, and available for market distribution on demand. Members can set specific API keys to ensure that uploaded files reache the market securely.  4. Develop Customer Markets with Decibels Media Marketing Features Once a creator's files are distributed and securely posted to networks such as YouTube, where the Decibels secure Codex eliminates media theft during MP4 Conversion, creators can begin to build the value of their markets through file views, sales, and exchanges when selected features are activated.  5. Inform Audiences Decibels helps creators to keep audiences informed of new media file additions on the Decibels platform, ensuring that customers never miss the latest and best creations.  6. Receive Earnings Proceeds from each sale are instantly added to the creator's Decibels wallet, where they can either be stored, or exchanged for other currencies and transferred to external wallet addresses. Creators also have the option to reinvest their DCBL tokens via advertising and promotion on the Decibels website.  ROADMAP ______________     TOKEN DETAILS ______________   . Author: DecibelsICO
Title: [ANN][ICO] ğŸ›° Decibels ğŸ›° - Decentralized Digital Royalties System
Body: Currently, there aren't any competitors seeking what our development will offer. There is Viberate which is offering a marketplace for live music industry, but doesn't come close to the market we plan to target. Viberate is limited to the growth of live music and concerts, we don't plan to take on this market what so ever. Our market that we are reaching out to is far less limited to the date and time of live music.  Theta Token is a great observation, but again, they seem to target the issue with YouTube and video content delivery. Although this would be something I would be interested in expanding to, it ultimately isn't the market I am going after either. My plan is to tackle the growing creative market, coupled with the ever expanding tech market. More is to come in our white paper. In the mean time, just know that we are have done our research on current ICO's and we wouldn't waste our time, money, or effort on a development that would over-saturate a already filled marketplace. We are taking extreme care to pay keen attention to market trends and how the creative market influences the technical market and vice-versa.  This will be next level and will have the potential to be implemented in places such as vehicles, mobile/tablets, computers, movies, music, and much much more. Again, we aren't tackling one issue. We are tackling THE issue.
